Deg [[tusnakt]], [[Tasɣent]] d tafekka tasnakant i d-isgensisen [[assaɣ imisin]] i teqqnen yal aferdis seg [[tagruma]] yettwassmman [[tagruma n tbadut]] neɣ tagrawt n tbadut neɣ taɣult <math>X \!</math> s yiwen n uferdis deg tegrawt yettusemman [[tazdaɣult]] neɣ taɣult tamudemt. Neɣ s usemres n taftart tasnakant tamaddudt: <math>f\colon X \rightarrow Y,x \mapsto f(x) \!</math>

Seg usenmel-a, ttwafarasen-tt-d waṭas n tɣawsiwin tigejdanin:
* I yal amsedfar [[tagruma n tbadut|tagrawt tabadut]] tettwasemma <math>X \!</math>.
* I yal amsedfar n tegrawt n tezdaɣult tettwasemma <math>Y\!</math>.
* Ulamek ɣef uferdis seg tegrawt n tagruma <math>X \!</math> ad tettwaqqen anagar s uferdis amyiwen seg tegrawt n tezdaɣult  <math>Y \!</math>.
* Aferdis seg tegrawt n tezdaɣult  <math>Y \!</math> yezmer ad yettwiqqen s yiwen n uferdis neɣ ugar seg tegrawt n tegruma <math>X \!</math>.

Ma tella tegruma d tagrawt n wazalen  i yezmer umeskil imziregad yawi <math>x</math>, ihi tazdaɣult d tagrawt n wazalen unẓiren i wazalen n tesɣent <math>f(x)\!</math>.

